{"data":[{"date":"15:26 22/08","title":"Messi v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 \u0111i ch\u01a1i bi\u1ec3n c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh Suarez","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/messi-va-vo-di-choi-bien-cung-gia-dinh-suarez.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5780","checkdouble":"195076"},{"date":"13:20 22/08","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ea1nh tranh Rabiot c\u00f9ng Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/ac-milan-muon-mua-adrien-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Barcelona, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Andres Iniesta.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rabiot mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi PSG</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Paris Saint-Germain c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Thomas Tuchel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAdrien Rabiot c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi PSG ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2019. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi gia h\u1ea1n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/ac-milan-muon-mua-adrien-rabiot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRabiot mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Barcelona \u0111ang v\u1eaby g\u1ecdi trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u201cd\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00e0\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Milan v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n giao cho c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Elliott, AC Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn. V\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng nu\u1ed1t l\u1eddi khi mang v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n San Siro m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 ra \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Mattia Caldara, Gonzalo Higuain, Samu Castillejo, Diego Laxalt, Tiemou\u00e9 Bakayoko, Ivan Strinic\u2026 T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, Milan \u0111\u00e3 chi 110 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Milan l\u00e0 Leonardo hi\u1ec3u r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 Rabiot do \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1ea1i PSG. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng Rossoneri c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMilan \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 PSG d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m sau \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Rabiot d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bakayoko-tri-an-chelsea-sau-khi-gia-nhap-ac-milan-184-194523.html\">Bakayoko tri \u00e2n Chelsea sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-ac-milan-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-chelsea-172-194493.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AC Milan chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/milan-chi-dam-mua-milinkovicsavic-176-194463.html\">V\u00ec \u201ctrung \u00fay\u201d Savic, Milan s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-xit-chelsea-ky-hop-dong-voi-ac-milan-trong-vai-gio-toi-172-194417.html\">Bom x\u1ecbt Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-chi-110-trieu-euro-mua-milinkovicsavic-176-194386.html\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5779","checkdouble":"195061"},{"date":"13:45 22/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nho-cay-bac-si-han-quoc-chua-tri-cho-hung-dung.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u00e1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t l\u00ean VFF \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u00e1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-muon-tien-ve-Do-Hung-Dung-sang-Han-Quoc--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n\u00a0nh\u1edd c\u1eady b\u00e1c s\u0129 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb cho H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia tay \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t l\u00ean VFF \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n y khoa th\u1ec3 thao ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u trang b\u1ecb m\u00e1y m\u00f3c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n Anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129 Choi Ju-young. \u00d4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \"th\u1ea7n y\" trong l\u00e0ng y h\u1ecdc th\u1ec3 thao H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Park Ji-sung, Lee Dong-gook.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m \u1edf H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, theo c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 6 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran-168-195062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran-168-195062.html\">Son Heung-min n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Olympic Iran?</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Bahrain: K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5778","checkdouble":"195065"},{"date":"14:24 22/08","title":"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau \"th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda\" ASIAD 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-noi-gi-sau-tham-hoa-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD sau 24 n\u0103m. V\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u00f4ng Worrawoot Srimaka \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/photo1534897180665-1534897180666670647944.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan, Worrawoot Srimaka g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi NHM sau k\u1ef3 ASIAD &quot;th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda&quot;&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Qatar.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, Th\u00e1i Lan g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bangladesh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uzbekistan \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a 'nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa voi chi\u1ebfn' \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn NHM n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn d\u1eef. Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT) sa th\u1ea3i HLV Srimaka v\u00e0 m\u1eddi Kiatisuk Senamuang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 U23 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn c\u1ee7a NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7u xin s\u1ef1 tha th\u1ee9 t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Srimaka c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 'tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t' t\u1eeb L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan song \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda FAT, ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (21/8), ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT) Somyot Poompunmuang \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi r\u1eb1ng Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng sa th\u1ea3i HLV Srimaka b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t t\u1ea1i Indonesia. Theo \u00f4ng, vi\u1ec7c thay HLV kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Srimaka t\u1eebng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i U22 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch SEA Games 29 th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Kiatisak. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Srimaka kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nho-cay-bac-si-han-quoc-chua-tri-cho-hung-dung-168-195065.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nho-cay-bac-si-han-quoc-chua-tri-cho-hung-dung.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nho-cay-bac-si-han-quoc-chua-tri-cho-hung-dung-168-195065.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u00e1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t l\u00ean VFF \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran-168-195062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran-168-195062.html\">Son Heung-min n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Olympic Iran?</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5777","checkdouble":"195068"},{"date":"15:09 22/08","title":"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean \"m\u00e2y xanh\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Kim chi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>B\u00e1o H\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean \"m\u00e2y xanh\"</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean m\u00e2y xanh sau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean m\u00e2y xanh sau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Bao-Han-tiep-tuc-dua-HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-len-may-xanh-sau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, h\u00e3ng th\u00f4ng t\u1ea5n Yonhap (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn: \"NHM Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0i nghi khi HLV Park Hang-seo c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 l\u00fd do c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00ean l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam, sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Yonhap cho bi\u1ebft: \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 g\u1eb7p Bahrain v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23 t\u1edbi. H\u1ecd to\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bahrain \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u1edbi cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\".</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd b\u00e1o Donga l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 HLV Hiddink t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng Gi\u00eang \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ede Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a HLV Guus Hiddink t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c k\u1ef3 World Cup 2002\u2026\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-noi-gi-sau-tham-hoa-asiad-2018-168-195068.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-noi-gi-sau-tham-hoa-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-noi-gi-sau-tham-hoa-asiad-2018-168-195068.html\">HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD sau 24 n\u0103m. V\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u00f4ng Worrawoot Srimaka \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran-168-195062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-dai-chien-voi-olympic-iran-168-195062.html\">Son Heung-min n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Olympic Iran?</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5776","checkdouble":"195073"},{"date":"17:47 22/08","title":"\"Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/viet-nam-can-tan-cong-phu-dau-truoc-bahrain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD 2018, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 g\u1ee3i \u00fd v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i c\u1ea5p ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Bahrain, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c, BLV V\u0169 Quang Huy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quang Huy cho bi\u1ebft, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Bahrain b\u1edfi h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 11 b\u1eadc tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 Saudi Arabia, Iraq hay UAE, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1eeda tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, trong khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u00ecn m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb&rdquo; &ndash; BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Zing.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean, ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ngay t\u1eeb khi nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i e ng\u1ea1i Bahrain. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia tay gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc khi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot-168-195087.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot-168-195087.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Bahrain: S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Park Hang...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh-168-195073.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh-168-195073.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean m\u00e2y xanh</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Kim chi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Bahrain: K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5775","checkdouble":"195086"},{"date":"17:25 22/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Bahrain: S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out ASIAD 2018, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mong mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng ri\u00eang g\u00ec v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Bahrain t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1c quan l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u00e0o su\u1ed1t 270 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Doi-hinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Bahrain-Su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 3 trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang 'bay cao' \u1edf ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 3 trung v\u1ec7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0103n \u00fd v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 3 n\u00e0y \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u00e0ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u00e0n nh\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal, khi m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u00edt khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Bahrain v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Song ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 \u00f4ng Park mang t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0i to\u00e0n \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain, b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c hay trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eefu D\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tranh ch\u1ea5p, anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i nguy h\u1ea1i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e8 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc Huy va Xuan Truong da cap tai U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-Ai-se-sat-canh-cung-tien-ve-Xuan-Truong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c, kinh nghi\u1ec7m hay kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p th\u00ec \u0110\u1ee9c Huy c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4, tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n \u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quang H\u1ea3i hay Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh thay ph\u1ea7n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Sau hai tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 99% Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c m\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &quot;c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh&quot; c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo cho v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Xuan Truong\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo &quot;c\u1ea5t k\u1ef9&quot; cho v\u00f2ng 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bahrain. T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL, v\u00e0 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i mai 23/8. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 \u00e1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/Doi-hinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh-168-195073.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh-168-195073.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean m\u00e2y xanh</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Kim chi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Bahrain: K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5774","checkdouble":"195087"},{"date":"17:49 22/08","title":"Lewandowski gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/22/robert-lewandowski-phat-bieu-ve-bayern-munich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai t\u1ea1i CLB, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9ng ra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lewandowski kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bayern</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRobert Lewandowski chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Bayern Munich t\u1eeb Dortmund m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 155 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 197 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho Bayern.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19, Lewandowski c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n sau 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eintracht Frankfurt t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Drochtersen t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/robert-lewandowski-phat-bieu-ve-bayern-munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Lewandowski mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c. \u201cV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4, th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00f4i\u201d, Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich tr\u00ean Sport Bild.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed9c khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CLB. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o trong 2, 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9t nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed5i l\u1eeda thi\u00eau ch\u00e1y t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3 c\u00e1c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee9ng ra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb \u1edf Munich trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ngu\u00f4i ngoai ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot-193-194414.html\">Bayern Munich nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski-193-194398.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real v\u00e0 M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-frankfurt-05-bayern-munich-sieu-cup-duc-2018-330-194360.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Frankfurt 0-5 Bayern Munich (Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-dam-phan-chieu-mo-boateng-197-194077.html\">PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5773","checkdouble":"195085"},{"date":"15:25 22/08","title":"Real Madrid chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/real-madrid-chuan-bi-gui-loi-de-nghi-cuoi-cung-vu-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n, theo Daily Mirror, Real Madrid chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/real-madrid-chuan-bi-gui-loi-de-nghi-cuoi-cung-vu-eden-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, nh\u01b0ng The Blues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. HLV Sarri quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-194831.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard</span> g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi th\u00eam \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n, theo Daily Mirror, Real Madrid chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi th\u00eam \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n chi t\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991, Real \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 d\u00f9 Hazard ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat do ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng Chelsea v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n. HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi anh t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Hazard th\u00ec Real c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Marcos Alonso c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Marcelo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5772","checkdouble":"195067"},{"date":"16:06 22/08","title":"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng HLV Klopp v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Naby Keita","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/khoi-dau-an-tuong-hlv-klopp-van-doi-hoi-nhieu-hon-tu-naby-keita.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Naby Keita, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Naby Keita ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba James Milner, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Georginio Wijnaldum \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. T\u00e2n binh Naby Keita d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi The Kop nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Naby Keita va Sadio Mane gio tai ngo trong mau ao Liverpool.\" title=\"Naby Keita v\u00e0 Sadio Mane gi\u1edd t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/nguoi-cu-chi-ra-yeu-to-giup-liverpool-co-the-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-mua-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Naby Keita ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Naby Keita ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, anh tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u1eeb h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. Van Dijk khen ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 52,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool b\u1ecf ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Naby Keita, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Naby Keita</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Naby Keita, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp doi hoi nhieu hon tu Naby Keita\" title=\"HLV Klopp \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Naby Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/khoi-dau-an-tuong-hlv-klopp-van-doi-hoi-nhieu-hon-tu-naby-keita.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Naby Keita</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00edch \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Naby Keita tham gia v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong ph\u1ea1m vi h\u1eb9p, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Keita s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool, Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp Brighton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5771","checkdouble":"195077"},{"date":"16:30 22/08","title":"Chelsea c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid v\u1ee5 Marcos Alonso","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia La Liga quan t\u00e2m Alonso</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Alonso ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga mu\u1ed1n Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga mu\u1ed1n Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Alonso ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/marcos-alonso-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-180-182943.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marcos Alonso</span>, Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u1eb1m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf La Liga hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean Chelsea \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea khong ban Marcos Alonso\" title=\"Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/chelsea-khong-ban-marcos-alonso.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra \u0111i. Chelsea s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Alonso.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield 3-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 Arsenal 3-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Alonso \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i mang v\u1ec1 1 qu\u1ea3 11m, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5770","checkdouble":"195078"},{"date":"16:14 22/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Jorginho sau kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u01a1 \u1edf Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/nguoi-dai-dien-tang-boc-jorginho-sau-khoi-dau-trong-mo-o-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Jorginho t\u1ea1i Chelsea kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean b\u1edfi \u201cc\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp kh\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri c\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Joao Santos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/nguoi-dai-dien-tang-boc-jorginho-sau-khoi-dau-trong-mo-cung-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Chelsea r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfng Anh r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Jorginho kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Chelsea c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t th\u00ec c\u1eadu ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Chelsea kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn derby London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Jorginho r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal. C\u00f3 t\u1edbi 50 C\u0110V t\u1eeb Napoli \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 xin ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh sau tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau Naples v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef t\u00ecnh y\u00eau n\u00e0y. S\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00f9 Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi London&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso-172-195078.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid v\u1ee5 Marcos Alonso</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-piazon-sap-roi-chelsea-172-195071.html\">&ldquo;H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i&rdquo; Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb sang Ligue 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5769","checkdouble":"195082"},{"date":"17:20 22/08","title":"Wilshere: \u201cArsenal \u0111\u00e3 sai khi ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf t\u00f4i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/wilshere-phat-bieu-ve-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng West Ham gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai khi \u0111\u1ea9y anh ra \u0111i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Arsenal quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Jack Wilshere. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u00e0 anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, Wilshere li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Anh ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/wilshere-phat-bieu-ve-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd sai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger, Wilshere t\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Mikel Arteta s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Unai Emery m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 Wilshere ra \u0111i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi West Ham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng minh Arsenal sai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 11 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal, Jack Wilshere chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB c\u0169 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh s\u00e2n Emirates t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 3 Premier League. Nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai khi h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cArsenal \u0111\u00e3 sai khi ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf t\u00f4i. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d, Wilshere n\u00f3i. \u201cS\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn Emirates v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Bolton hay Bournemouth.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWest Ham \u0111ang kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 khi thua l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bournemouth. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Wilshere t\u1ef1 tin h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho Arsenal, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd\u201d, Wilshere n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a West Ham.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/manchester-dang-tro-thanh-mot-arsenalwenger-thu-hai-172-195074.html\">Manchester \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Arsenal-Wenger th\u1ee9 hai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neville-arsenal-khong-dang-nhan-nhung-chi-trich-172-195070.html\">Neville: Arsenal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-khong-ngai-tram-cong-than-arsenal-172-195069.html\">Emery kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3m c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-yeu-cau-arsenal-tuc-toc-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-ramsey-172-195042.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i gi\u1ee5c Arsenal t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-van-chua-the-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-ramsey-vi-172-195040.html\">Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey v\u00ec...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-dang-phai-chien-dau-cho-tuong-lai-o-arsenal-172-195031.html\">Ozil \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5768","checkdouble":"195084"}]}